headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Auto Shop Bonuses
content:
Increase your Auto Shop's legit profits this week by fulfilling vehicle upgrade requests from clients in Auto Shop Client Jobs. Deliver these vehicles as ordered or kick it up a notch with your own custom configuration and have faith the client shares your vision to earn 2X GTA$ and RP.

Exotic Exports are also dealing out 2X GTA$ and RP for successful deliveries. Check your daily list of vehicles on the blackboard in the Auto Shop and look out for these high-end exports in Freemode.
